title: Windows 8.1 Preview Bundle
description:
Windows 8.1 Preview Bundle
==========================

This bundle is part of my OS bundle collection (you can 
view them all at https://thepiratebay.se/user/makdir2). 
The OS bundle collection contains bundles from Windows 7
 up to Windows 10 Preview.

It contains the following files:

* WidnowsBlue-ClientwithApps-32bit-English-X1899604.iso
* WindowsBlue-ClientwithApps-64bit-English-X1899605.iso
* info.txt
* Windows-8.1-Preview-Bundle--md5-list.chks

The product key for the provided .iso images is

> NTTX3-RV7VB-T7X7F-WQYYY-9Y92F

You can check the files using md5sum like this:

$ md5sum -c ./Windows-8.1-Preview-Bundle--md5-list.chks

Or just compare the md5 checksums you generate from the
 downloaded files to these (same order as above):

* 23862c4495579ba48573fb4088677cbb
* a46318a1234a1f454e1518a2fd31651d
* db417a0d88ca68248493cf6072a69453
   This last one (of 'info.txt') can be different

Thanks for downloading 'Windows 8.1 Preview Bundle' and
 keep seeding! :)
